cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with hand gesture recognition using deep learning models for wearable devices. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also likely as the paper proposes a gestural interface for smartphones and video see-through head mounts. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with video datasets and real-time performance on mobile devices. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning models for gesture recognition. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with the retrieval of information through hand gestures.
